### Get all categories (for dropdown)
GET http://localhost:3000/products/categories

###

### Get all products (public)
GET http://localhost:3000/products

###

### Get products with filters
GET http://localhost:3000/products?category=Casual&minPrice=10&maxPrice=100&page=1&limit=12

###

### Get products by category
GET http://localhost:3000/products/category/Casual

###

### Search products
GET http://localhost:3000/products?search=shirt

###

### Get specific product by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE

###

### Create a new product (Admin/Super Admin only) - First login as admin
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### Register an admin user first (if needed)
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123",
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "User"
}

