###

### Create product with JSON (Admin/Super Admin only)
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Formal Blazer",
  "description": "Elegant blazer for formal occasions",
  "price": 89.99,
  "category": "Formal",
  "sizes": ["S", "M", "L", "XL"],
  "colors": ["Black", "Navy", "Gray"],
  "stock": 50
}

###

### Update product (Admin/Super Admin only)
PUT http://localhost:3000/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Product Name",
  "price": 39.99,
  "salePrice": 29.99
}

###

### Delete product (Admin/Super Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

###

### Get product statistics (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/products/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

###

### Get low stock products (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/products/admin/low-stock?threshold=10
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN

###

### Delete product image (Admin/Super Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE/images
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageUrl": "https://cloudinary-url-here"
}

